posed to have a fill rate on the order of about 40 screens worth of pixels in 240p20 with most effects turned on?  Including alpha?<br /><br />I admit I forgot about fill rate in my enthusiasm for the polygons per scene metric, which is embarrassing as fill rate is well known as a major bottleneck on N64.  That does limit things a bit...</div>

