					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p198066">Re: Breath of the Wild on N64?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=198066&amp;sid=6d7e202bbc6e9e722ab2e5e3f90ff3fc#p198066"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Jun 12, 2017 4:53 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
