				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p198140">Re: Breath of the Wild on N64?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=198140&amp;sid=6d7e202bbc6e9e722ab2e5e3f90ff3fc#p198140"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Tue Jun 13, 2017 3:11 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
